com.lampaderum.service

Class StreetlampQueryService

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jhipster.service.QueryService<Streetlamp>
      • com.lampaderum.service.StreetlampQueryService

  • @Service
 @Transactional(readOnly=true)
public class StreetlampQueryService
extends io.github.jhipster.service.QueryService<Streetlamp>
    Service for executing complex queries for Streetlamp entities in the database. The main input is a StreetlampCriteria which gets converted to Specification, in a way that all the filters must apply. It returns a List of StreetlampDTO or a Page of StreetlampDTO which fulfills the criteria.
